HEADWORD: Cinque-pace
<hw>Cinque"-pace`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Cinque</ets> + <ets>pace</ets>.]</ety> <def>A lively dance
(called also <altname>galliard</altname>), the steps of which were
regulated by the number five.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Nares.
Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
